metadata.name: Apathy
metadata.description:
"Happy pills" took her sadness away but they gave her apathy, insomnia, migraine, tremor, nausea, dry mouth, lack of libido, diarrhea, impaired vision, weight gain, constipation, sleepiness, drowsiness, clumsiness, nervousness, sweat, restlessness, fatigue, muscle spasms, drooling, etc...

Note: If you're struggling with depression, mood swings or any kind of mental health issue please seek the help of a medical professional!

AI + embroidery on medicine blister packs + digital art
4000 X 4000px
